metadata.description: Deep inside the jungles of Colombia, a young guerrilla rebel turns rogue in an effort to avenge her tortured past and free a people from the grips of war. An introductory book showcasing characters and plot points. Written by Andrew Vannata with art by Chadwick Coleman ("Faxia Preta") and Antonio J. Rojo ("JFH: Justice For Hire").
